            <lg xml:id="TK481">
<l>pakalvelluṅ kūkaiyaik kākkai yikalvellum</l>
<l>vēntarkku vēṇṭum poḻutu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A crow will overcome an owl in the day time so the king who would conquer his enemy must have (a suitable) time.</l>
            </lg>
